    dc:description "FIGURES 12 – 16. 12. Macrophasma n. gen. biroi (Redtenbacher, 1908), Ψ (coll. FH). 13. Macrophasma n. gen. biroi (Redtenbacher, 1908), PLT ♂ (ZMUH). 14. Macrophasma n. gen. oreithrephes (Günther, 1929), Ψ (coll. FH). 15. Macrophasma n. gen. lyrata (Redtenbacher, 1908), Ψ (RMNH). 16. Stephanacris laeviceps n. sp., HT Ψ (RMNH)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173444/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173445>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 22. 17. Stephanacris draconius n. sp., HT Ψ (ZSMC). 18. Stephanacris multilobatus n. sp., PT Ψ (Coll. FH). 19 – 22. Eggs [scale = 1 mm]. 19. Stephanacris draconius n. sp. PT, dorsolateral view (ZSMC). 20. Stephanacris multilobatus n. sp. PT, dorsolateral view (coll. FH). 21. Stephanacris laeviceps n. sp. PT, dorsolateral view (RMNH). 22. Macrophasma n. gen. biroi (Redtenbacher, 1908), dorsolateral view (coll. FH)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173445/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

